The paper focuses on the impact of IoT devices on interpersonal relationships in multi-occupant households, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the study involves collecting and analyzing data, which could also fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), systems and control (cs.SD), and computing and society (cs.CC).
